libbc-concurrency (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial public release.
  * Worker pool: MPMC queue-backed, configurable worker count,
    per-slot lifetime callbacks.
  * Typed dispatch and shared cross-worker context.
  * Signal-safe shutdown coordination.
  * Full sanitizer coverage (asan / tsan / ubsan / memcheck) and
    cppcheck-clean sources.

